name: Damnation
description:
Above the door of Hell, a door that no virtuous soul passes through, an inscription : "Through me, one enters the domain of pain... It is Justice which inspired my sublime creator... You who enter here, lose all hope." 

Indeed, the punishments inflicted on the damned are perpetual. Pronounced for eternity, they leave no hope of redemption.
